{"tid":1803284,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"係時候用暗黑文宣了-幫中共稱霸全球","createTime":"2019-12-30T05:55:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-30T06:03:08.000Z","uid":184099,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"c560fa32a27217d79f5dd82bc023944e9d21ef74","tid":1803284,"uid":184099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T05:55:13.000Z","msg":"近日，<br />\n小弟開左數個twitter同fb，<br />\n<br />\n四處宣揚中國下一步要消滅某某國，<br />\n要稱霸全球，<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">再貼出中國各種軍事，經濟等硬實力。耀我國威。</span></strong></span><br />\n竟然吸引無數中共小紅粉捧場。<br />\n隨後加入戰隊攻擊其他國家。<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">已經令好多國家既網民反感。</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但好似好少人咁做。<br />\n對內，有品蔥用「加速主義」宣揚愛國。<br />\n對外，用「暗黑文宣」耀我國威。<br />\n<br />\n希望各位加入暗黑文宣戰隊。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36c731ff502b9d583f3f1eac620d91387ef8000b","tid":1803284,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T05:57:41.000Z","msg":"有諗過用大量未FC料搞亂牆內<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"054fda29d62860b5ed4380d826ee8cdab0357657","tid":1803284,"uid":273218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T05:58:40.000Z","msg":"不嬲都有做<br />\n我會用英文話<br />\n中美貿易戰<br />\n杜指一日唔見500點<br />\n支那已成美國大佬"},{"pid":"7e5dae2b9c4706d2e4cc352fc0f7c9850a041849","tid":1803284,"uid":305536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T06:03:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>德國聯署有三份  呢家仲有一份未達標 <span style=\"color: red;\">最後兩日</span><br />\n<br />\n德國減少對中國和其他非民主國家的依賴<br />\n<a href=\"https://epetitionen.bundestag.de/petitionen/_2019/_09/_01/Petition_98731.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fepetitionen.bundestag.de%2Fpetitionen%2F_